Q(6): What kind assistance do you need? 

A: Health Care? 
	Q(6.1):  Check out the Veteran Health Care page [http://www.va.gov/health] If you need help Email Argos at ArgosRemembers@gmail.com or call Anthony at (781) 241-3286
A: Financial Assistance?
	Q(6.2): Depending on your income you may qualify for Chapter 115 Cash Aid Benefits through your city. Why don't you connect with Argos Remembers and set up an appointment. Email Argos at ArgosRemembers@gmail.com or call Anthony at (781) 241-3286
A: Suicide Prevention?
	Q(6.3): Call 911 of go to  [https://www.veteranscrisisline.net] for help. 
A: Education Benefits? 
	Q(6.4): Education Benefits are some of the best benefits offered to Veterans. You should Email Argos at ArgosRemembers@gmail.com or call Anthony at (781) 241-3286 to discuss how to utilize the benefits you have to reach your goals. 
A: Home Loan? 
